The following configuration successfully builds the package:

Compiler:
    GCC 4.8.1 or
    Intel C++ Composer XE 14.0 SP1 Update 1

Third-party libraries:
    GSL 1.16
    OpenBLAS 0.2.8
    SuiteSparse 4.2.1
    sqlitepp 0.2            (included in libs/, works e.g. with sqlite3 3.7.17)
    cln 1.3.3
    fftw 3.3.3
    
Optional dependencies:
    png++ 0.2.5             (included in libs/, works e.g. with libpng 1.5)
    OpenMPI
    OpenCL

